assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: SKM Egg Products Export (India) Limited produces and sells eggs and egg products. The company offers various egg powders, including whole egg powder for use in biscuits, cakes, bakery mixes, pasta, sauces, dressings, ready meals, quiches, omelettes, mayonnaise, meat products, and other emulsified systems; egg yolk powder for use in mayonnaise, dressings, sauces, Spanish bread, croissants, pasta, and ice-cream; and egg albumen powder for use in meat and fish products. It also provides bakery mix products for use in cheese cakes, biscuits, cakes, sponge cakes, Swiss rolls, etc.; and liquid eggs comprising whole egg liquids, egg yolk liquids, egg albumen liquids, and customized egg liquids for use in cakes, meringues, noodles, mayonnaise, bakeries, fine food, ice-creams, cosmetics, confectionery, and pastries. In addition, the company trades in feed ingredients. It serves in Russia, Europe, Japan, Indonesia, Thailand, Vietnam, Malaysia, Taiwan, Nigeria, the United Arab Emirates, India, and Saudi Arabia. SKM Egg Products Export (India) Limited was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Erode, India.
